PN,37301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784654322
OL,3,CBoss of London's bus network 'shocked'
OL,4,Cto hear drivers using bottle as a
OL,5,Ctoilet
OL,7,FThe boss of London's bus network said
OL,8,Fshe was shocked by the findings of an
OL,9,FITV News London investigation which
OL,10,Frevealed how drivers went to the
OL,11,Ftoilet in a bottle.
OL,13,FLorna Murphy, who is Transport for
OL,14,FLondon's Director of Buses, said she
OL,15,Fwanted to ensure every route had
OL,16,Faccess to basic hygiene facilities.
OL,18,FShe explained there were currently
OL,19,Ffive routes without access to a
OL,20,Fdedicated toilet, but Ms Murphy
OL,21,Fpledged that would change this year.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/21
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784654322
OL,3,CBoss of London's bus network 'shocked'
OL,4,Cto hear drivers using bottle as a
OL,5,Ctoilet
OL,7,F"Nobody should have to go to the
OL,8,Ftoilet in a scenario such as the one
OL,9,Fdescribed," Lorna Murphy told ITV News
OL,10,FLondon.
OL,12,F"It was a shock given that we do have
OL,13,Ftoilet facilities on all but five
OL,14,Froutes ` and those five do have
OL,15,Falternatives in terms of local shops
OL,16,For restaurants, etc.
OL,18,F"But I certainly never want anybody to
OL,19,Fhave to do that."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/21
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784654322
OL,3,CBoss of London's bus network 'shocked'
OL,4,Cto hear drivers using bottle as a
OL,5,Ctoilet
OL,7,FShe highlighted recent investment to
OL,8,Fopen more toilets in important
OL,9,Flocations, such as the end of routes
OL,10,For where one driver takes over from
OL,11,Fanother, adding: "There has been a
OL,12,Fdedicated programme of investment
OL,13,Fsince 2017 where several million
OL,14,Fpounds has been spent putting in new
OL,15,Ftoilet facilities."
OL,17,FTransport for London (TfL) manages a
OL,18,Ffleet of around 9,000 buses operating
OL,19,Fon around 675 routes across the
OL,20,Fcapital.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/21
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784654322
OL,3,CBoss of London's bus network 'shocked'
OL,4,Cto hear drivers using bottle as a
OL,5,Ctoilet
OL,7,FMost services are run by private
OL,8,Foperators who sign a contract with
OL,9,FTfL. Asked if they were doing a good
OL,10,Fjob, Lorna Murphy said: "They are
OL,11,Fwanting to do the right thing and
OL,12,Ftrying very hard to do well in a
OL,13,Fdifficult operating environment.
OL,15,F"London is a difficult operating
OL,16,Fenvironment, but everyone is working
OL,17,Ftogether to make conditions for bus
OL,18,Fdrivers as good as they can be."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/21
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784654322
OL,3,CBoss of London's bus network 'shocked'
OL,4,Cto hear drivers using bottle as a
OL,5,Ctoilet
OL,7,FTransport for London said it had ways
OL,8,Fto check whether bus companies were
OL,9,Fdelivering on the terms of their
OL,10,Fcontracts.
OL,12,FBut the problems for workers are not
OL,13,Flimited to toilets. London has been
OL,14,Fsweltering in a heatwave and
OL,15,Ftemperatures in bus drivers' cabs can
OL,16,Freportedly reach 40C.
OL,26,@xD@TOX
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/21
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784654322
OL,3,CBoss of London's bus network 'shocked'
OL,4,Cto hear drivers using bottle as a
OL,5,Ctoilet
OL,7,FLast week, the Labour MP for Enfield
OL,8,FNorth said London's bus drivers had
OL,9,F"borne the brunt" of the extreme heat
OL,10,Fin the city, and Lorna Murphy
OL,11,Facknowledged they had faced a "really
OL,12,Fchallenging few weeks".
OL,14,FShe said keeping buses cool presented
OL,15,Fa number of challenges, but some
OL,16,Fprogress had already been made.
OL,18,F"There's been no let-up and that's
OL,19,Freally hard for everybody to deal with
OL,20,Fpersonally," Ms Murphy said.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/21
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784654322
OL,3,CBoss of London's bus network 'shocked'
OL,4,Cto hear drivers using bottle as a
OL,5,Ctoilet
OL,7,F"It's also difficult for vehicles and
OL,8,Ffor systems. Over the last few years
OL,9,Fwe have changed our vehicle
OL,10,Fspecification. We have brought in
OL,11,Fbetter, more highly rated air
OL,12,Fconditioning for drivers in their cabs
OL,13,Fand also for customers.
OL,15,F"It is really difficult because buses
OL,16,Fhave so many windows and doors are
OL,17,Fopening and closing regularly.
OL,19,F"So keeping the temperature as cool as
OL,20,Fyou might expect in your car, for
OL,21,Fexample, is difficult.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/21
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784654322
OL,3,CBoss of London's bus network 'shocked'
OL,4,Cto hear drivers using bottle as a
OL,5,Ctoilet
OL,7,F"But our new specification does go a
OL,8,Flot further than what was there before
OL,9,Fand we have had really good feedback
OL,10,Ffrom drivers of those vehicles, which
OL,11,Fis really positive.
OL,13,F"We've introduced a new task force
OL,14,Fwhich met for the first time last
OL,15,Fweek, and we'll continue to meet
OL,16,Fregularly going forward."
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/21
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784654322
OL,3,CBoss of London's bus network 'shocked'
OL,4,Cto hear drivers using bottle as a
OL,5,Ctoilet
OL,7,FITV News London was given a recording
OL,8,Fof a driver who was laughed at by an
OL,9,Fofficial when they complained the bus
OL,10,Fwas too hot.
OL,12,FLondon's Mayor, Sadiq Khan, said
OL,13,Fdrivers should not risk their personal
OL,14,Fsafety and said anyone who thinks
OL,15,Ftheir bus is too hot "must stop" and
OL,16,Fnot worry about following their usual
OL,17,Ftimetable.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/21
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784654322
OL,3,CBoss of London's bus network 'shocked'
OL,4,Cto hear drivers using bottle as a
OL,5,Ctoilet
OL,7,FAsked about the recording, Lorna
OL,8,FMurphy said: "I'd really encourage
OL,9,Fthat driver to bring that recording to
OL,10,Fus so we can investigate it properly.
OL,12,F"I do think that the vast majority of
OL,13,Fpeople are trying to do the right
OL,14,Fthing and it's possible that
OL,15,Fsomething's gone wrong here or
OL,16,Fsomething's been taken out of context.
OL,18,F"But fundamentally we've been very
OL,19,Fclear that people should be allowed to
OL,20,Ftake a break if they need it.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/21
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784654322
OL,3,CBoss of London's bus network 'shocked'
OL,4,Cto hear drivers using bottle as a
OL,5,Ctoilet
OL,7,F"If they get too hot, we know that
OL,8,Fit's been really hot out there and the
OL,9,Fconditions in the cab are hot.
OL,11,F"People need to be able to take a
OL,12,Fcomfort break if they need it, and
OL,13,Fthat comfort break needs to be as long
OL,14,Fas they need to get back to a position
OL,15,Fwhere they are able to drive."
OL,17,FTransport for London said all buses
OL,18,Fhave air conditioning to some extent
OL,19,Fin the driver's cab, but older buses
OL,20,Fcannot lower the temperature enough in
OL,21,Fvery hot weather.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/21
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784654322
OL,3,CBoss of London's bus network 'shocked'
OL,4,Cto hear drivers using bottle as a
OL,5,Ctoilet
OL,7,FThis can make it seem as though the
OL,8,Fsystem is broken.
OL,10,F"What we are also doing is carrying
OL,11,Fout a series of audits of vehicles to
OL,12,Fmake sure the technology is working as
OL,13,Fit should," Lorna Murphy explained.
OL,15,F"One of the actions through the task
OL,16,Fforce is to look at whether we can
OL,17,Fretrofit those older buses with the
OL,18,Fnewer technology, which could be a
OL,19,Fgood way of moving us forward.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/21
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784654322
OL,3,CBoss of London's bus network 'shocked'
OL,4,Cto hear drivers using bottle as a
OL,5,Ctoilet
OL,7,F"Doing that to several thousand buses
OL,8,Fwon't be able to happen overnight, so
OL,9,Fwe'll have to work through that as a
OL,10,Fprogramme.
OL,12,F"There's more coming and we have more
OL,13,Fnew buses coming every day as well, so
OL,14,Fthe conditions will get easier," she
OL,15,Fadded.
OL,17,FIn addition to hot buses and a lack of
OL,18,Ftoilets, ITV News London also revealed
OL,19,Fhow drivers were falling asleep behind
OL,20,Fthe wheel at traffic lights.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G13/21
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784654322
OL,3,CBoss of London's bus network 'shocked'
OL,4,Cto hear drivers using bottle as a
OL,5,Ctoilet
OL,7,FThey complained gruelling rotas, long
OL,8,Fhours and short turnaround times had
OL,9,Fcaused them to nod off while working.
OL,11,FTransport for London said it knew
OL,12,Ffatigue was an issue and was exploring
OL,13,Fways to tackle tiredness.
OL,15,FAsked what she was doing, Lorna Murphy
OL,16,Fsaid: "Clearly we're a safety-critical
OL,17,Findustry and therefore it really
OL,18,Fmatters, and it's something we've been
OL,19,Fworking on for a long time.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G14/21
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784654322
OL,3,CBoss of London's bus network 'shocked'
OL,4,Cto hear drivers using bottle as a
OL,5,Ctoilet
OL,7,F"There's been a lot of money invested
OL,8,Fin different things around education
OL,9,Fand health.
OL,11,F"There have also been developments
OL,12,Faround technology and what we're
OL,13,Freally trying to do is learn so we can
OL,14,Fhave a data-driven approach to what we
OL,15,Fdo next.
OL,17,F"And that's our entire approach to bus
OL,18,Fsafety and, in reality, all things
OL,19,Fsafety. We want to know exactly what
OL,20,Fis causing it and when it is happening.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G15/21
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37316
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784654322
OL,3,CBoss of London's bus network 'shocked'
OL,4,Cto hear drivers using bottle as a
OL,5,Ctoilet
OL,7,F"And the latest fatigue detection
OL,8,Ftechnology that we have installed on
OL,9,F400 buses will help us with that data.
OL,11,F"So we'll be able to see, for example,
OL,12,Fif it is more likely to happen on the
OL,13,Fsecond day back after rest days, then
OL,14,Fperhaps that duty needs to be shorter
OL,15,For have more breaks in it, or whatever
OL,16,Fit might be, but it will come from the
OL,17,Fdata.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G16/21
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37317
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784654322
OL,3,CBoss of London's bus network 'shocked'
OL,4,Cto hear drivers using bottle as a
OL,5,Ctoilet
OL,7,F"At the moment, a lot of the
OL,8,Finformation we have is subjective. It
OL,9,Fvaries from person to person when you
OL,10,Fspeak to people about it. So we really
OL,11,Fwant to gather that data so we can do
OL,12,Fthe right thing."
OL,14,FBus drivers have been calling on
OL,15,FTransport for London and bus companies
OL,16,Fto introduce a series of protections
OL,17,Finto their contracts that they say
OL,18,Fwould help make their jobs safer and
OL,19,Fimprove the way they work.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G17/21
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37318
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784654322
OL,3,CBoss of London's bus network 'shocked'
OL,4,Cto hear drivers using bottle as a
OL,5,Ctoilet
OL,7,FLondon Assembly members agreed a
OL,8,Fmotion for a "Bill of Rights" that
OL,9,Fwould see contractual protections for
OL,10,Fdrivers.
OL,12,FIt includes proper rest breaks, safe
OL,13,Fand well-maintained vehicles, and
OL,14,Ftoilet and welfare facilities on
OL,15,Froutes.
OL,17,FBut Ms Murphy said the points already
OL,18,Fexisted, whether in health and safety
OL,19,Flegislation, employment law or within
OL,20,Fexisting contracts.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G18/21
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37319
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784654322
OL,3,CBoss of London's bus network 'shocked'
OL,4,Cto hear drivers using bottle as a
OL,5,Ctoilet
OL,7,FLooking ahead, TfL's Director of Buses
OL,8,Fsaid she wanted to see several hundred
OL,9,Fmore zero-emission buses on London's
OL,10,Fstreets in 12 months' time.
OL,12,F"We'll be much further forward in
OL,13,Fterms of decarbonising our network and
OL,14,Freducing emissions in London," Lorna
OL,15,FMurphy said.
OL,17,F"Those buses will have better air
OL,18,Fconditioning for drivers and
OL,19,Fcustomers, and also the latest safety
OL,20,Ftechnology and systems.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G19/21
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37320
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784654322
OL,3,CBoss of London's bus network 'shocked'
OL,4,Cto hear drivers using bottle as a
OL,5,Ctoilet
OL,7,F"So that will be a really key step
OL,8,Fforward.
OL,10,F"I think we'll have implemented the
OL,11,Factions agreed by the task force,
OL,12,Fwhich will be a really positive step
OL,13,Fforward for everybody concerned.
OL,15,F"And I'd like to think that some of
OL,16,Fthose would be replicated outside
OL,17,FLondon as well.
OL,19,F"And then finally, I think it would be
OL,20,Fgreat if we could see an increase in
OL,21,Four commendations for drivers.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G20/21
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37321
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784654322
OL,3,CBoss of London's bus network 'shocked'
OL,4,Cto hear drivers using bottle as a
OL,5,Ctoilet
